            "heading": "PRODUCT DESCRIPTION",
            "open": false,
            "content": "<p>Imagine moving freely again…<br/>Through narrow streets, sandy beaches, forest paths — anywhere life takes you.</p><p>With <strong>Momplush</strong>, every outing becomes lighter, smoother, and beautifully simple.</p><p>Designed for modern parents who value both <strong>comfort and connection</strong>, this toddler carrier brings your child closer while giving you back your freedom. No more struggling with bulky strollers — just effortless movement, wherever you go.</p><p>Crafted from <strong>100% natural cotton</strong>, it feels soft, breathable, and gentle against your child’s skin, while remaining strong enough for everyday adventures. Lightweight and easy to carry, it adapts seamlessly to every season.</p><p>Its intuitive design allows you to <strong>carry your child in seconds</strong>. No adjustments, no stress — just a natural, balanced fit. Whether you’re left- or right-handed, Momplush moves with you.</p><h3>Why parents choose Momplush ?</h3><ul><li><strong>Instant use</strong> – On and off in seconds</li><li><strong>Lightweight & compact</strong> – Folds easily, perfect for travel</li><li><strong>Ergonomic comfort</strong> – Designed for both parent and child</li><li><strong>Freedom over strollers</strong> – Go where wheels can’t</li><li><strong>Perfect for toddlers</strong> – From 9 months to 4 years (up to 20 kg / 44 lbs)</li><li><strong>Certified safety</strong> – Tested to meet strict quality standards</li><li><strong>Eco-conscious</strong> – Minimal plastic packaging<br/></li></ul><h3>Product Details :</h3><ul><li>Suitable for children from <strong>9 months to 4 years</strong> (max. 20 kg)</li><li>Seat made from <strong>100% cotton</strong></li><li>Strap made from <strong>polyester</strong></li><li>Durable clip in <strong>PU</strong></li><li>Premium finishing details (logo varies by colour)</li><li>Universal design, suitable for all caregivers<br/></li></ul><p><em>Please note: Colours may appear slightly different depending on lighting and screen settings.</em></p>",
            "page": "",
            "custom_liquid": ""
          }
        },
